,"msg":"時光返不到最初　<br />\n回憶一天天錯過<br />\n難以對你再親口說下承諾<br />\n墓碑的旁邊　<br />\n我即使向你談論今天的鎖碎<br />\n你都不覆半句&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"4fc69a06e3461814e9c6f1788c47fbdbef893179","tid":14812,"uid":10038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:24:54.000Z","msg":"沒關係你也不用給我機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f545e628ed04983ace41b2cedfb6c38521781b1c","tid":14812,"uid":21707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:24:59.000Z","msg":"你還要我怎樣 要怎樣<br />\n你突然來的短信就夠我悲傷<br />\n我沒能力遺忘 你不用提醒我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f3b9f0341770261a2c0f52967bef5cb96cf2317","tid":14812,"uid":31602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:25:06.000Z","msg":"為何未能讓我死去便要認識你"},{"pid":"7aa73703872b24028d1d0c00f11bc4af4b4d4dae","tid":14812,"uid":16957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:25:20.000Z","msg":"說了再見以後 - 蘇打綠 <br />\n<br />\n低頭想找你，卻只剩倒影。<br />\n我試著騙自己，有散也有聚，<br />\n只是想起了，再無人聆聽，不如歸去。<br />\n<br />\n諗親呢幾句 就根本連喊嘅心情都冇"},{"pid":"5d4fe371465f32cd2e407213ca950ee6c8cd0064","tid":14812,"uid":15080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:26:45.000Z","msg":"但時你這種條件 哪會理解這一種層面<br />\nCome on james <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a4ac18abcb3a8492e3e5b1b2a41c24262368599","tid":14812,"uid":15080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:27:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但是你這種條件 哪會理解這一種層面<br />\nCome on james <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4484e2778efb29b0b83dd6c2750c903973f5050d","tid":14812,"uid":8900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:27:32.000Z","msg":"歌: 結果<br />\n<br />\n啊 不管傾出幾多 仍然是這樣結果<br />\n<br />\n何必編織那一起的夢 雙手給我<br />\n<br />\n悔不當初 簡簡單單一個"},{"pid":"99c2e73ff64b820f791becfae4f7df6b56edc210","tid":14812,"uid":21262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:28:22.000Z","msg":"我沒有為你傷春悲秋不配有憾事<br />\n<br />\n個人認為軒仔首春秋係一首被埋沒左既出色兵歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe57533492297c177399578dc4d5cfecf8a08db","tid":14812,"uid":21707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:32:38.000Z","msg":"可惜不是你 陪我到最後 曾一起走卻走失那路口<br />\n<br />\n可惜不是你 成首<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n訓啦唉 <br />\n現已夜深，請幾陰道收細<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a4a43231f9f846b01a8e66b35d30924d6c15650","tid":14812,"uid":21615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:36:49.000Z","msg":"你依舊 住在我的 回憶裡不 出來 <br />\n我離開 將你的手 交給下個 最愛 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7e4c7aab3fe35362dfdeb829313e5e56e37a24","tid":14812,"uid":33979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:39:04.000Z","msg":"並沒什麼我愛上的不愛我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad61d8622b6ff0027c75428880ecf4519d5f308","tid":14812,"uid":3098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:43:41.000Z","msg":"愛不到我最想要愛的人 誰還能要我怎樣呢<br />\n我愛的人 不是我的愛人 <br />\n她心裡每一寸 都屬於另一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a8e1ae578c1f710d1cf565ac35bacc54aa4e1c","tid":14812,"uid":45182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:47:46.000Z","msg":"你要離開 我知道很簡單<br />\n你說依賴 是我們的阻礙<br />\n就算分開 但能不能別沒收我的愛<br />\n當作我最後才明白"},{"pid":"46203ad5ba207b7ea80c0203ae4bdcf4fb7d63ad","tid":14812,"uid":43853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:52:50.000Z","msg":"歌:好人<br />\n詞:說穿了我不美 I am alone I am alone I am alone I am alone I am alone I am alon