的依賴<br />\n還有誰能叫我勇敢<br />\n除了你之外的空白<br />\n還有誰能來教我愛"},{"pid":"4a84d14a269963a0b440c20571164e782d53ac7b","tid":14812,"uid":43853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T20:12:08.000Z","msg":"好想喊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31789f793dd385ce13cfb0061766602a925841dc","tid":14812,"uid":33929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T20:41:28.000Z","msg":"寧願失戀亦不想失禮 難道要對著你力歇聲嘶"},{"pid":"08e3d5eb92c502915767bba2b183ec01ae9ff6c7","tid":14812,"uid":34645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T20:42:30.000Z","msg":"你用含過別人雞巴的嘴說愛我<br />\n我用舔過別人咪咪的嘴說要跟你結婚"},{"pid":"0c410f3c72c94d267803200fe1d4375f99347f0f","tid":14812,"uid":26878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T20:54:31.000Z","msg":"當一眾好友至親 需要一個替身 通通找我如御用陪襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4f9bb57388faf522733cda5f289940b04e5a3b3","tid":14812,"uid":9288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T21:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/01/050433_0f146bb131b5cc9a8f24ec4eeedd53fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F01%2F050433_0f146bb131b5cc9a8f24ec4eeedd53fc.jpg&h=0fc4c7b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75c902b6f8d52604952a875f8389b6115f4924b1","tid":14812,"uid":9288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T21:05:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/01/050433_0f146bb131b5cc9a8f24ec4eeedd53fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https:/